pr_title: Unity setup documentation and sample project to visualise the MPM results
pr_body:
This has all the files required to reproduce the unity project for visualising the MPM output.

**Describe the PR**
This PR adds a guideline to visualise the results in a Unity scene.

**Additional context**
This work was done as part of GSoc 2022

**Related Issues/PRs**
